Hi Lucy, 
I didn't see this until now but I will take all the feedback you and Jasmine gave into consideration when editing the rest of my portfolio. Thanks for showing my work to her :grinning:

Since those pages were from my personal notebook, do you think it would be better to do a neater redraw of the content displayed there and replace it entirely, or include both the neater one and the  original pages together

I'm aware that it is up to me in the end, but regardless of that, I still want to hear your opinion on this matter
